            <h2 class="title-info">被韩国“宠着”的农民 | 图集</h2>
            <div class="author-info" data-spm="author-info">

                <a class="info" href="http://m.sohu.com/media/658437">
                    <img class="avatar"
                    src="http://sucimg.itc.cn/avatarimg/39d76bec52f6421d9f178eb275da5f14_1512960932413"/>
                    <div class="infos-wrapper">
                        <header class="name">鉴闻</header>
                        <footer class="time">
                            09-10 09:45
                        </footer>
                    </div>
                </a>
                <footer class="follow" 
                data-spm-acode="3401"
